523
00:36:59,615 --> 00:37:01,649
<i>The witnesses are in Iran.</i>

524
00:37:01,650 --> 00:37:05,323
<i>And the people who are accused
are in Iran.</i>

525
00:37:05,324 --> 00:37:10,724
