to any of that.

526
00:37:10,725 --> 00:37:14,024
<i>That makes pursuing
a criminal investigation</i>

527
00:37:14,025 --> 00:37:17,291
<i>from outside of Iran
very difficult.</i>

528
00:37:16,570 --> 00:37:20,866
The 752 case is not about air safety.

