00:38:13,377 --> 00:38:17,005
We have a right to be present...

546
00:38:17,130 --> 00:38:20,175
in any examination
of the black boxes.

547
00:38:20,300 --> 00:38:23,720
We will not surrender them to others.

548
00:38:24,095 --> 00:38:26,162
Once you’ve had a situation

