(SNIFFLING)

1153
01:21:16,830 --> 01:21:20,438
(LIGHT CLANKING)

1154
01:21:33,550 --> 01:21:35,992
January 6th.

1155
01:21:36,223 --> 01:21:39,126
(SPEAKING IN FARSI)

1156
01:21:39,127 --> 01:21:42,790
(CLANKING)

1157
01:21:47,960 --> 01:21:51,370
(SCRAPING)

1158
01:21:53,504 --> 01:21:56,969
(FESTIVE MUSIC PLAYING
ON COMPUTER)

1159
01:22:00,313 --> 01:22:02,183
