Exchanges of fire...</i>

1230
01:29:36,472 --> 01:29:38,264
Full-scale invasion
of Ukraine...

1231
01:29:38,265 --> 01:29:41,740
<i>The largest invasion
of a neighbouring
country in Europe.</i>

1232
01:29:41,741 --> 01:29:46,107
<i>(REPORTER 3): Russian troops are
closing in on the capital.</i>

1233
01:29:46,108 --> 01:29:47,647
